      "author_email": "raouf@gazaskygeeks.com",
      "body": "Dimensions has two main business branches:\nIT and Digital Transformation\nConsulting\nThe company has an APEX solution tailored for the health sector.\nTheir client base includes major clients in Palestine, Africa, and Cyprus.\nSome of their key clients include:\nIstishari Hospital Group\nMajor clinics and health centers in Palestine\nThe company works with two types of clients:\nProject-based clients\nYearly contract-based clients\nAll of the company’s systems are developed internally by their IT team.\nThe company is currently facing challenges in Palestine, as the health sector has been heavily affected after the war.\nOne of the key challenges is that many local clients are not paying on time or are not fully committing to the payment terms stated in their contracts.\nAs a result, the company has experienced a 50% drop in revenue from the local market.\nDespite these challenges, the company did not lay off any employees during the war, and no salary deductions were applied to staff.\nThe company has recently formed a new AI team and is interested in receiving support in this area.\nThey are currently focused on expanding into international markets and securing new clients outside Palestine, with target markets including:\nSaudi Arabia\nQatar\nAfrica (especially Angola)\nEurope\nThis company appears to be a strong fit for the Marketing & Branding intervention.\nMarketing & Branding support needs include:\nWebsite development and optimization\nContent creation\nBranding support\nUpskilling needs include:\nAutomated QA training for 5 resources\nAI skills training for 5 resources\nSoft skills training, with details to be shared later\nC-Suite support needed:\nProject Management\nPriority list:\nMarket Access / Expansion\nMarketing & Branding",
      "source": "raouf-docx"
    },
